storyInfo: The two operators work together with the Felynes to deal with a massive herd of hornbeasts. On the other end, a familiar voice began to urge on the old hunter.

attributes.content: Scholar, get up a tree, quick! There's a herd of hornbeasts coming!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: There's no time! Yato!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm doing what I can!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Mrow! Something stinky fur mew!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Arty, what did you just throw?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Blegh! Stinks like hell! Did those fowlbeasts come back again?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It's having an effect! The herd is changing direction!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: What did you use, Artisan?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Fowlbeast, stinky! Made Dung Bomb!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Ah, so that was it! Of course my little Smithy would be able to craft a Dung Bomb from droppings so quickly!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: If you throw a Dung Bomb onto a monster, they won't be able to stand the smell and will run away from mew, just like us with Noir Corne earlier.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Hey, no using me as an example!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Even though they changed directions, they're still rampaging through the forest. This will be troublesome if the Rathalos tracks get trampled over.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Rampaging hornbeasts... I feel like that's definitely out of the ordinary. Why would they go berserk for no reason?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It doesn't matter, we just need to stop them.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: With my expurrtise, I postulate that there must be a lead hornbeast at the front to make such a huge herd move like that.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Really now? If that's the case, then we'll just have to cut it down.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Wait, what do you mean by 'just have to cut it down'?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: What part of that was hard to understand?
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: And how exactly do you plan to do that, huh?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Just charge right in.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: There's so many of them and they're all in a frenzy... You sure about that? We don't even know why they're going crazy.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: And will they wait for us to sit down and figure out the cause? Cover me.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Wait up! Arty, do you still have that, uh... Dung Bomb?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: So much stinky! Fur mew!
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: Scholar, I just want to make sure... If I can land this on the lead hornbeast, is it possible the rest of them will disperse?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Based to their purr-evious reaction... In theory.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: But pawbably not fur long! And you have to aim from up close to make sure it hits the right one.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Aight, I think I got something. I'll try and aim for it from up here on the tree.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Yato, when the other hornbeasts scatter, take the chance and subdue the leader in one strike!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Of course I will.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: But this means you'll...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Get even stinkier? Eh, couldn't be any worse—yuck!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: There's... still time...
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: They are too fast, too young, too powerful, too difficult to control.
The past once suppressed surges forth, yet the danger of the forest has never abated.
You have lost control, broken your body, made too many mistakes.
No!
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: No... that's not the reason.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: We must keep up the chase.
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Ah, isn't that...?
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.content: Over there! I spotted it!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Right in furont of the stampede, the one with bigger horns and a yellow sheen to its fur, that should be the lead beast!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: It's heading here.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: I can do this, I can do this...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Focus.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: They're almost here, get ready.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Wait... I think I dropped my nose plug.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Now!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Huh? Argh! Forget it!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Super Dung Bomb Attack! Right on target!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: —Haah!
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: ...Did you get it?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Got it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Sure enough, the herd has calmed down quite a bit.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Corne, you...
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Yes, I know! I stink like hell, I'll get away from you guys!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No, you're hurt.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Oh, this scratch? It's nothing.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: It's a good thing I had a spare first aid kit. Come over here and I'll take care of it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Ah... O-Okay.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Come over quick, the two of mew.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: See here? The nose of the lead beast has traces of a grayish white dust here.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Uh, this looks familiar...
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Back home, there is a species of fauna known as a Stinkmink that can release a cloud of pheromones, sending meownsters into a frenzy and charging straight into mew.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Our Hunters make use of that effect in their hunts.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Ah, now I remember... I saw bottles of this stuff at that Kashiwau's place, could it be...?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: I'm pawsitive.
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Did he know we entered the forest and agitate the hornbeasts with the dust to cut us off?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: He did say 'Don't ever let me see you there—'
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: No, that can't be it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Huh?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: He was already in the forest by yesterday afternoon, while we only arrived here after the incident in the cave, so he shouldn't know our whereabouts.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: He couldn't have seen us in the forest either; there's no way I wouldn't have spotted him first.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: True enough, and I guess if his motive was to find the Rathalos, he wouldn't want to risk losing its tracks either, by triggering such a stampede.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Lemme think... Or maybe he planned to do something else with the herd, but lost control of it?
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: ...You're thinking about pointless things again. We have a beast to track.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: This is bad! Smithy's gone again!
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: We were together in the tree earlier, but when we came down...
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Ahhh! I won't go through that ever again... never!
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Mrrow...
attributes.name: Felyne Artisan

attributes.content: I think I heard a Felyne over there.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: Ah! Smithy! What happened to mew?
attributes.name: Felyne Scholar

attributes.content: Seems like... he got stunned by the stink.
attributes.name: Noir Corne

attributes.content: ...I can only hope this will be the worst of it.
attributes.name: Yato

attributes.content: Today's sun is setting.
Look...The light between the leaves wavers, while their rustling in the darkness grows ever louder.
A momentary impulse... O beasts who have gone astray.
You will not return from the darkness of the forest.
Shut up...
attributes.name: Yoshitaka Kashiwau

attributes.text: Our equipment...has been sabotaged...unable to display normally...
